{"tid":1452051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無文宣幫幫手，我要全世界同班垃圾斷交！","createTime":"2019-08-11T23:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:00:22.000Z","uid":305378,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"201f8fd127ad018cdd39fd12b074741460e2b9f4","tid":1452051,"uid":305378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:35:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾曾經自稱二戰猶太人俾人屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20170224-dailynews-hk-police/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20170224-dailynews-hk-police%2F&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=0aae3124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20170224-dailynews-hk-police/</a><br />\n<br />\n琴晚嬲到瞓唔着，有冇人可以將琴日情況發過去以色列同德國嘅報紙編輯，比佢哋睇吓自稱猶太人，但係做緊蓋世太保嘅社會人渣垃圾嘅所作所為<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我完全唔想再比呢班社會垃圾有任何國際形象</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f35101adb7e069c3dd7174ee498447b6ce1b110","tid":1452051,"uid":305378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:35:48.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ed323040e25d5dc1176199c92b8d96361ed876d5","tid":1452051,"uid":305378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:36:48.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"9374c6ab41ba47ce24f4df25f216e8cf9c30cb8f","tid":1452051,"uid":305378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:37:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f9770f54cffaefbc609d9a360b3735b5eb280389","tid":1452051,"uid":266341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7af26b7b539c09070586ac7b960c30796a0922c9","tid":1452051,"uid":305378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:38:15.000Z","msg":"P牌都要推"},{"pid":"60be11559fcb490f6329c57ae60c055f2d63adae","tid":1452051,"uid":305378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:38:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9f1d6c23b2ed20834a18436